  "title": "Senior Florist/Floral Designer",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Senior Florist/Floral Designer</p><p>Company: The Flower Factory</p><p>Location: Joo Chiat/Ubi, Singapore</p><p>Employment Type: Full-time<br /></p><p><strong>About The Flower Factory</strong></p><p>The Flower Factory is a leading florist in Singapore founded in 2013. Our team believes in hard work, positive energy, and a passion for beautiful things. Led by an experienced entrepreneur with multiple successful exits, we're expanding beyond flower into new business areas, an exciting opportunity for those who want to learn and grow.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>At least 2 years of working experience as a Florist. Skilled in different floral styles (modern, classic, wedding, corporate).</p></li><li><p>Hardworking and responsible, with a strong willingness to learn.</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ol><li><p>Strong pay package with great career growth prospects: Be part of a company that's evolving beyond floral business into multiple business ventures.</p></li></ol><ol><li><p>Mentorship from an Experienced CEO: Learn directly from a founder with multiple successful exits - ideal for fresh graduates or individuals eager to gain hands-on business and retail experience.</p></li><li><p>Supportive Team Culture: Work with a passionate, hardworking yet down-to-earth team.<br /></p><p>Interested candidates please do not apply here; send your resume along with your works to 81639692 via WhatsApp. Applications here will not be processed.</p></li></ol>",
